ygData.messageBody:
OK this made me think of a question. Does anyone know what lvl Amanda
Brightblaze (or Something Brightblaze) in Butcherblock is? She is at the 2
little buildings right before the GF zeon. She doesn't like Gnome Necros
I'll tell you that, did 118 dmg to me in 1 freakin hit!!!! I made it to
zone w/ 30 HP LEFT! and thanks GOD for Shieldskin. hehe anyway I want to
come back someday and SLAY HER! She pissed me off killed me once when I was
8th and the most recent time I was about to zone and someone had pulled her
to the GF zone! DOH!
SHE MUST DIE!!?!? Anyone know what lvl she is?
